(1, 'DEAL American Journey Salmon & Sweet Potato Recipe Grain-Free Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46839_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603634_.jpg', 'American Journey is full of nutritious ingredients that fuel your pets everyday adventures. The Salmon & Sweet Potato Recipe Grain-Free Dry Dog Food formula features real, deboned salmon with the protein and amino acids your dog needs for leaner muscles, and the exceptional flavor she instinctively craves. Delicious sweet potatoes and chickpeas are included to give your pup energy that lasts. With wholesome fruits and veggies like carrots, dried kelp and blueberries, your dog is getting beneficial fiber, phytonutrients and antioxidants. Omega fatty acids are plentiful, including DHA, an omega-3 that supports healthy development of the brain and eyes. These omegas come from several sources like salmon oil and flaxseed, and they help keep your fellow adventurers skin and coat healthy. This recipe is grain-free and has no corn, wheat or soy, which makes it a great choice for dogs that are prone to food sensitivities.', 100, 0, 16.99),
(2, 'Blue Buffalo Life Protection Formula Adult Chicken & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46839_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603634_.jpg', 'Blue Buffalo Life Protection Formula was created for the holistic health and well-being of adult dogs. All formulas start with real meat, whole grains, garden veggies and fruit, plus added LifeSource Bits, a precise blend of nutrients that have been enhanced with a Super 7 package of antioxidant-rich ingredients. This Adult Chicken & Brown Rice Recipe features delicious, protein-rich deboned chicken and other natural ingredients for a healthy meal your dog will love.', 100, 0, 9.99),
(3, 'Wellness TruFood Baked Nuggets Adult Recipe with Chicken & Chicken Liver Grain-Free Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46839_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603634_.jpg', 'Wellness believes in giving pets a colorful palette of the best nutrition possible, so they made TruFood with whole foods from farm, field and sea. TruFood has more of what pets need to be vibrant and happy - that's how love becomes Wellness. It\'s clear from the moment you peek through the side of the bag that Baked Blends is made from fresh, whole-foods that can support your dog\'s immune and digestive systems as well as their joints, skin and coat. Wellness starts with whole-prey chicken and adds fiber like peas, chickpeas and lentils, antioxidant-rich superfoods like beets and blueberries, real air-dried fruits and vegetables, and flaxseed to create a well-balanced, delicious meal.', 100, 0, 16.31),
(4, 'Triumph Grain-Free Turkey, Pea & Sweet Potato Recipe Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/51505_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1531945998_.jpg', 'Triumph super premium grain-free recipes appeal to dog\'s natural ancestral instincts and cravings. With real meat, easy to digest carbohydrates and select vegetables and fruits, these recipes are both healthy and holistic. And best of all, your dog will love the great taste!', 100, 0, 16.11),
(5, 'The Honest Kitchen Instant Pumpkin Spice Latte for Dogs & Cats, 4-oz jar', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/catalog/108419_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1486751054_.jpg', 'Everyone loves a sweet, warming pumpkin spice latte when its chilly outside, and now your best friend can enjoy one made just for her with The Honest Kitchen Instant Pumpkin Spice Latte for Dogs & Cats. Recommended for dogs and cats of all ages, this 100% human-grade formula features a nourishing fusion of fall flavors. A restorative blend of goats milk, pumpkin, honey, cinnamon and ginger, its perfect as a delicious drink, for hydrating The Honest Kitchen foods, or poured over dry kibble as a special liquid treat. This all-natural, seasonal edition supplement is made in the USA by a family-owned company and is completely free of by-products, preservatives or GMO ingredients.', 100, 0, 16.31),
(6, 'The Honest Kitchen Instant Eggnog for Dogs & Cats, 4-oz jar', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/57599_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1508430947_.jpg', 'No holiday celebration is complete without a cup of sweet, delicious eggnog, and now your best friend can enjoy a cup made just for him with The Honest Kitchen Instant Eggnog for Dogs & Cats. Recommended for dogs and cats of all ages, this 100% human-grade formula features a nourishing fusion of festive holiday flavors. A restorative blend of goats milk, egg, honey and cinnamon, its perfect as a delectable drink, for hydrating The Honest Kitchen foods, or poured over dry kibble as a special liquid treat. This all-natural, seasonal edition supplement is made in the USA by a family-owned company and is completely free of by-products, preservatives or GMO ingredients.', 100, 0, 18.81),
(7, 'Taste of the Wild Pacific Stream Grain-Free Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/49068_MAIN._AC_SL1500_V1524669774_.jpg', 'Nourish your furry friend with the balanced diet nature intended when you feed him Taste of the Wild Pacific Stream Grain-Free Dry Dog Food. Formulated with novel proteins including real smoked salmon, this grain-free recipe includes peas and sweet potatoes that deliver the highly-digestible energy your active pup needs, along with natural antioxidant support from real fruits and vegetables and dried chicory root for prebiotic support and healthy digestion. Essential minerals are chelated with amino acids to optimize their absorption and ensure maximum benefit, for complete and balanced nutrition with a taste of the wild your furry pal will crave.', 100, 0, 28.49),
(8, 'Taste of the Wild Pacific Stream Puppy Formula Grain-Free Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/catalog/108427_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1486750972_.jpg', 'Nourish your puppy pal with the balanced diet nature intended with Taste of the Wild Pacific Stream Puppy Formula Grain-Free Dry Dog Food! Formulated with novel proteins including salmon, this grain-free recipe includes peas and sweet potatoes that deliver the highly-digestible energy your growing puppy needs, along with natural antioxidant support from real fruits and vegetables and dried chicory root for prebiotic support and healthy digestion. Essential minerals are chelated with amino acids to optimize their absorption and ensure maximum benefit, for complete and balanced nutrition with a taste of the wild your furry friend constantly craves!', 100, 0, 30.99),
(9, 'Chicken Soup for the Soul Puppy Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46882_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603871_.jpg', 'Chicken Soup for the Soul knows how important food is for your dogs well-being. Through innovative formulas filled with premium nutrition, your dog can stay happy, healthy and well. The Puppy Dry Dog Food captures the warmth of comfort food and is made from only the highest quality ingredients. Its specially created for a growing puppy, and contains antioxidants and DHA for proper eye and brain development. Served with love, this nutritionally balanced food will promote lifelong health for years of barking and belly rubs.', 100, 0, 24.67),
(10, 'American Journey Chicken & Sweet Potato Recipe Grain-Free Puppy Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/50460_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1508430539_.jpg', 'American Journey is full of nutritious ingredients that fuel your growing puppys everyday adventures. The Chicken & Sweet Potato Recipe Grain-Free Puppy Dry Dog Food formula features real, deboned chicken with the protein and amino acids your puppy needs to keep her growing muscles lean. Its made to meet her specific nutritional requirements, and has the exceptional flavor she instinctively craves. Delicious sweet potatoes and chickpeas are included to give your developing pup energy that lasts. With wholesome fruits and veggies like carrots, dried kelp and blueberries, your dog is getting beneficial fiber, phytonutrients and antioxidants. Omega fatty acids are plentiful, including DHA, an omega-3 that supports healthy development of the brain and eyes. These omegas come from several sources like salmon oil and flaxseed, and they help keep your fellow adventurers skin and coat healthy. This recipe is grain-free and has no corn, wheat or soy, which makes it a great choice for puppies that are prone to food sensitivities.', 100, 0, 24.99),
(11, 'American Journey Chicken & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46839_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603634_.jpg', 'American Journey is full of nutritious ingredients that fuel your pets everyday adventures. The Chicken & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food formula features real, deboned chicken as the first ingredient, plus wholesome grains and premium fruits and vegetables like carrots, blueberries and cranberries. This tasty recipe delivers protein for lean muscles and powerful antioxidants to help keep your dog feeling his best. You will find everything your dog needs to stay healthy tons of natural fibers for good digestion and plenty of omega fatty acids from several sources for skin and coat support. And its made without poultry by-product meal, wheat, corn or soy just the best ingredients with the most benefits for your dog.', 100, 0, 18.99),
(12, 'American Journey Beef & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/46839_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1529603634_.jpg', 'American Journey is full of nutritious ingredients that fuel your pets everyday adventures. The Beef & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food formula features real, deboned beef as the first ingredient, plus wholesome grains and premium fruits and vegetables like carrots, blueberries and cranberries. This tasty recipe delivers protein for lean muscles and powerful antioxidants to help keep your dog feeling his best. You will find everything your dog needs to stay healthy tons of natural fibers for good digestion and plenty of omega fatty acids from several sources for skin and coat support. And its made without poultry by-product meal, wheat, corn or soy just the best ingredients with the most benefits for your dog.', 100, 0, 22.99),
