(14, 'Stella & Chewys Chewy Chicken Meal Mixers Freeze-Dried Raw Dog Food Topper', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/51505_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1531945998_.jpg', 'Kickstart your canines kibble with Stella & Chewy\'s Chewy\'s Chicken Meal Mixers Freeze-Dried Raw Dog Food Topper. Delivering a boost of nutrition and yummy flavor, its an easy way to pack your poochs diet with nutrients, probiotics and antioxidants. Based on the philosophy that pets thrive on the same diet they would eat in the wild, this recipe gives your dog what she naturally craves, and is made from 95% cage free chicken, organs and bone plus 100% organic fruits and vegetables offering the benefits of raw food nutrition with the convenience of freeze-dried preparation. And to ensure the highest quality, each batch is made with care in Stella & Chewys own U.S. kitchen.', 100, 0, 38.99),
