(17, 'Stella & Chewys Savory Salmon & Cod Meal Mixers Freeze-Dried Raw Dog Food Topper', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/62299_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1526494705_.jpg ', 'Kickstart your canine\'s kibble with Stella & Chewy\'s Savory Salmon & Cod Meal Mixers Freeze-Dried Raw Dog Food Topper. Delivering a boost of nutrition and yummy flavor, it\'s an easy way to pack your pooch\'s diet with nutrients, probiotics and antioxidants. Based on the philosophy that pets thrive on the same diet they would eat in the wild, this recipe gives your dog what she naturally craves, and is made from 95% wild-caught salmon and cod including organs and bone, plus 100% organic fruits and vegetables-offering the benefits of raw food nutrition with the convenience of freeze-dried preparation. And to ensure the highest quality, each batch is made with care in Stella & Chewy\'s own U.S. kitchen.', 100, 0, 16.99),
