(20, 'American Journey Stews Poultry & Beef Variety Pack Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, 12.5-oz, case of 12', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/67512_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1535484156_.jpg', 'With American Journey Poultry & Beef Stews Variety Pack Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, your dog will get the nourishment he needs for any adventure the day might bring. Real chicken or beef starts off each recipe, followed by a savory broth to give dogs the tastes they crave plus high-quality protein to help them maintain lean muscles. These delicious stews are crafted in the USA with some of the world\'s finest ingredients from trusted sources. They\'re full of flavor but free of things like poultry by-product meal, grains, corn, wheat, soy and artificial colors, flavors and preservatives. You can count on these American Journey formulas to provide essential amino acids, plenty of omega fatty acids for skin and coat health, and added vitamins and minerals.', 100, 0, 19.99),
(21, 'American Journey Poultry & Beef Variety Pack Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, 12.5-oz, case of 12', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/51243_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1526494708_.jpg', 'With American Journey Poultry & Beef Variety Pack Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, your dog will get the nourishment he needs for any adventure the day might bring. Real meat starts off each recipe, followed by a savory broth to give dogs the tastes they crave plus high-quality protein to help them maintain lean muscles. These delicious loaf-style dinners are crafted in the USA with some of the world\'s finest ingredients from trusted sources. They\'re full of flavor but free of things like poultry by-product meal, grains, corn, wheat, soy and artificial colors, flavors and preservatives. You can count on these American Journey formulas to provide essential amino acids, plenty of omega fatty acids for skin and coat health, and added vitamins and minerals.', 100, 0, 19.99),
(22, 'American Journey Chicken & Turkey Recipe Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, 12.5-oz, case of 12', 'https://img.chewy.com/is/image/catalog/51243_MAIN._AC_SS190_V1526494708_.jpg', 'With American Journey Chicken & Turkey Recipe Grain-Free Canned Dog Food, your dog will get the nourishment he needs for any adventure the day might bring. Real chicken starts off the recipe, followed by savory chicken broth and mouthwatering turkey to give dogs the taste they crave plus high-quality protein to help them maintain lean muscles. This delicious loaf-style dinner is crafted in the USA with some of the world\'s finest ingredients from trusted sources. It\'s full of flavor but free of things like poultry by-product meal, grains, corn, wheat, soy and artificial colors, flavors and preservatives. You can count on this American Journey formula to provide essential amino acids, plenty of omega fatty acids for skin and coat health, and added vitamins and minerals.', 100, 0, 19.99);
